description: This Chainlink VRF common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 45, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 90, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Box for North, Nine Lives for East, 3 for South, and Leverage for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30452-49361-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [90 Votes, Common]
